OL,3,CMum's 'guilt' at persuading son to go
OL,4,Cto school on day he was stabbed
OL,6,FThe mother of Harvey Willgoose says
OL,7,Fshe feels "guilty" after revealing she
OL,8,Fpersuaded him to attend school on the
OL,9,Fday he was stabbed to death.
OL,11,FCaroline Willgoose said her 15-year-
OL,12,Fold son had regularly stayed away from
OL,13,FAll Saints Catholic High School in
OL,14,FSheffield, only attending about "14
OL,15,Fdays" during the last 16 months.
OL,17,FHarvey suffered a fatal stab wound to
OL,18,Fthe chest at the school on Monday, 3
OL,19,FFebruary. A 15-year-old boy has been
OL,20,Fcharged with murder.
