OL,3,CMum's 'guilt' at persuading son to go
OL,4,Cto school on day he was stabbed
OL,6,FHarvey had "lost so much weight"
OL,7,Fbecause of his anxiety about school,
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,F"I know that kids have got to go to
OL,11,Fschool but it needs looking at - it's
OL,12,Fnot for everybody," she said.
OL,14,FMrs Willgoose and her husband, Mark,
OL,15,Fhad a meeting with Sheffield City
OL,16,FCouncil's chief executive Kate Josephs
OL,17,Fon Wednesday as they stepped up their
OL,18,Fcampaign for improved safety in
OL,19,Fschools and better youth facilities.
