OL,3,CMum's 'guilt' at persuading son to go
OL,4,Cto school on day he was stabbed
OL,6,FThey said the support they had
OL,7,Freceived since their son's death had
OL,8,Fbeen "amazing".
OL,10,FMrs Willgoose said she was putting her
OL,11,F"life" into making a difference in
OL,12,Fhonour of "our Harvey".
OL,14,FAlong with knife arches in schools,
OL,15,Fthe couple want to see "youth clubs
OL,16,Fback".
