OL,3,CMum's 'guilt' at persuading son to go
OL,4,Cto school on day he was stabbed
OL,6,FHe said: "We've had these knife crimes
OL,7,Fgoing on for years and years and it's
OL,8,Fmade no difference. What needs to
OL,9,Fhappen now is what's going to make a
OL,10,Freal change. Somebody dying in school
OL,11,Fshouldn't happen - it has happened.
OL,12,FLet's look at what can be done to stop
OL,13,Fthis from happening again."
OL,15,FHarvey's funeral will be held at
OL,16,FSheffield Cathedral on Friday, 21
OL,17,FFebruary.
